---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base 
  title="About" 
  description="Meet the team behind Secunit Mercantile. Senior engineers with 20+ years of experience in cloud, security, and reliability."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold md:text-5xl">
          Built by Engineers Who've Been There
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
          We started Secunit Mercantile because small businesses deserve access to the same caliber of expertise that enterprises take for granted.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Photo placeholder -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-secondary/20 dark:from-darkmode-primary/20 dark:to-secondary/20">
            <div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="h-32 w-32 text-primary/40 dark:text-darkmode-primary/40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Social links -->
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <a 
              href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile" 
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-200 text-body transition-colors hover:bg-primary hover:text-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-darkmode-body dark:hover:bg-darkmode-primary"
              aria-label="LinkedIn"
            >
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a 
              href="https://github.com/x86txt" 
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-200 text-body transition-colors hover:bg-primary hover:text-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-darkmode-body dark:hover:bg-darkmode-primary"
              aria-label="GitHub"
            >
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a 
              href="mailto:matthew@secunit.io"
              class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-200 text-body transition-colors hover:bg-primary hover:text-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-darkmode-body dark:hover:bg-darkmode-primary"
              aria-label="Email"
            >
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
            Founder, Chief Geek
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Matthew Evans</h2>
          
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
            <p>
              I've spent over two decades designing, securing, and operating production systems for organizations where failure wasn't an option. My work has spanned hands-on engineering and executive leadership roles at companies including The Hartford, Cyware, Prometheus Alternative Investments, and earlier in my career IBM, Wells Fargo, AIG, and Honda Aircraft.
            </p>
            <p>
              My background sits at the intersection of security, reliability, and cloud engineering. I've led large-scale cloud migrations, built SOC2-aligned security and disaster recovery programs, and helped teams adopt DevOps and SRE practices that reduced outages, noise, and cost. I'm a CISSP and have served in acting CISO and director-level roles, working directly with executives while remaining deeply technical.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Why Section -->
          <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl bg-gray-50 p-6 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white">Why I started Secunit Mercantile</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
              Most small businesses don't need more tools or junior consultants — they need experienced guidance. I started Secunit Mercantile to give small and mid-sized companies access to senior-level security, DevOps, and reliability expertise without the overhead and pricing of large consulting firms. By operating as a fully remote, expatriate team, we deliver enterprise-grade outcomes at a cost that actually makes sense for growing businesses.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Credentials -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary dark:bg-darkmode-primary/10 dark:text-darkmode-primary">
              CISSP (since 2017)
            </span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-body dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-darkmode-body">
              20+ years experience
            </span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-body dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-darkmode-body">
              AWS & GCP
            </span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-body dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-darkmode-body">
              Kubernetes
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="container"><hr class="border-border dark:border-darkmode-border" /></div>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-3xl font-bold">The Team</h2>
      
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-4xl gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Matthew Card -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-secondary/20">
              <div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-primary/40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white">Matthew Evans</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">Founder, Chief Geek</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
                20+ years in cloud, security, and reliability engineering. CISSP since 2017.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Jason Card -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-secondary/20">
              <div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-primary/40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white">Jason Dinges</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">Senior Engineer</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
                Bio coming soon.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-3xl font-bold">How We Work</h2>
      
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
            <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white">Senior Expertise, Always</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
            You'll never be handed off to junior staff. Every engagement is led by experienced engineers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
            <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white">Clear Communication</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
            We explain technical concepts in plain language. You'll always understand what we're doing and why.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
            <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white">Practical, Not Perfect</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
            We focus on pragmatic solutions that fit your budget and timeline — not theoretical ideals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
            <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white">Your Success Is Our Success</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
            We operate as an extension of your team, not outside consultants. Your wins are our wins.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-2xl bg-primary p-8 text-center text-white md:p-12 dark:bg-darkmode-primary">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Let's Work Together</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg opacity-90">
          Ready to bring senior-level expertise to your team?
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn mt-8 bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100 dark:text-gray-900">
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
